message:
I have another idea : in my "base.html" i put my {% include "meta.html" %} in a block :

{% block meta %}{% include "meta.html" %}{% endblock %}

And in templates extending "base.html" where i need to change its content i can do

{% block meta %}
    {% with og_title="My page" %}
	{{ block.super }}
    {% endwith %}
{% endblock %}

And in my "meta.html" i can do

<meta property="og:title" content="{{ og_title|default:"Foo bar !" }}" />
